  "hasDecisionRecord": {
    "id": "https://uofa.net/nagaraja/decision/cou1-noncannulated-accepted-2026",
    "type": "DecisionRecord",
    "actor": "https://uofa.net/nagaraja/actor/credibility-assessment-team",
    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "Twelve of thirteen V&V 40 credibility factors meet or exceed the required gradation level for a Medium model risk, Medium decision consequence application. The single below-requirement factor (Test conditions, achieved Gradation 1 vs. required Gradation 2) was reviewed by the assessment team and judged acceptable given that: (1) all three QoIs satisfy both the E/uval < 1.96 and <10% percent difference acceptance criteria with margin; (2) the ASTM F1717 standard specifies a single canonical test configuration; and (3) the model is used only to predict performance under the same standard configuration. Overall credibility is sufficient to support the Accepted decision. Note: this package was generated under ProfileMinimal; the digital signature workflow is pending completion of the organizational PKI onboarding process. The sha256 hash provides content integrity verification in the interim.",
